extends AbstractValueWidget<T>
implements com.google.gwt.event.dom.client.HasChangeHandlers, com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.HasName, com.google.gwt.i18n.shared.HasDirectionEstimator, com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.HasText, com.google.gwt.i18n.client.AutoDirectionHandler.Target, com.google.gwt.editor.client.IsEditor<com.google.gwt.editor.ui.client.adapters.ValueBoxEditor<T>>, HasIcon, HasInputType, HasPlaceholder, HasCounter, HasReadOnly, HasActive

    UiBinder Usage:

      <m:MaterialTextBox placeholder="First Name" />

    kevzlou7979, Ben Dol, paulux84
